            <p>For oily skin, choose gel or lightweight lotion formulas. Dry skin benefits from richer creams with occlusive ingredients like shea butter or squalane. Combination skin may need different products for different areas, or a balanced formula that works for both. Don't forget your neck and décolletage—they need moisture too.</p>
            
