            <p>Remember, minimalism looks different for everyone. The goal isn't to have the sparsest home possible, but to create a space that feels right for you—calm, organized, and full of items that truly matter. Start where you are, make gradual changes, and find the level of minimalism that works for your lifestyle and brings you peace.</p>
