            <p>Porto's food scene is exceptional, with fresh seafood, traditional Portuguese dishes, and innovative modern cuisine. The francesinha, a local sandwich specialty, is a must-try. The city is also more affordable than Lisbon, making it an excellent value destination. Don't miss the Livraria Lello, one of the world's most beautiful bookstores.</p>
            
